title: White House On Lockdown, Obama Not On Grounds
text:
White House On Lockdown, Obama Not On Grounds Posted: 09/16/2015 03:09 PM EDT SAUL LOEB via Getty Images 
WASHINGTON, Sept 16 (Reuters) - The White House was placed on lockdown on Wednesday afternoon shortly after President Barack Obama left the grounds, Reuters witnesses said. 
No reason for the lockdown was immediately given. 
(Reporting by Lisa Lambert and Doina Chiacu; Editing by Bill Trott)
